episodes.title: "Bible-based" doesn't equate with "good"
episodes.description:
Welcome to the images that filled my young mind before going to bed each night.
Thank you, Watchtower Bible and Tract Society publications.

episodes.title: Why Witnesses believe ANYTHING printed by Watchtower
episodes.description: "What's New?" on JW.org is very illuminating. Let's explore the video "Promoting Love and Respect for Truth".

episodes.title: There is no problem that Watchtower Literature cannot solve (....or cause)
episodes.description: A recent e-mail from a family member got me to thinking about the unique relationship that Jehovah's Witnesses have with their own publications.
